- Add GDK_SMOOTH_SCROLL_MASK | GDK_SCROLL_MASK to webview for scroll events on GTK3/Wayland
- Debounce onWindowConfigure FFI callbacks to 50ms to prevent Bun crash during rapid resize
- resizeAutoSizingViews still called immediately for responsive UI
---
 package/src/native/linux/nativeWrapper.cpp | 98 +++++++++++++++++++---
 1 file changed, 86 insertions(+), 12 deletions(-)

diff --git a/package/src/native/linux/nativeWrapper.cpp b/package/src/native/linux/nativeWrapper.cpp
